Here is a summary of the transcript of, THE AGE OF A.I., S1, E1:  How Far is Too Far? The Age of A.I., using the NLP tool developed by Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory. The tool makes sense of the context by ranking keywords in the transcript and presents the most relevant content.  

"In some ways, the robotic drum arm allows Jason to play better than he ever has, but it still lacks the true function, or feeling, of a human hand...He's not just trying to clone a human, by any stretch, but trying to create an artificial stand-in that's somewhat believable..." 
